  Siong7-te3 e5 thiaN3 koh khah toa7: 
  Sui-jian5 pe7-bu2 e5 thiaN3 ui2-tai7, tan7-si7 iau2 u7 chit8 ui7 thiaN3 pi2 pe7-bu2 khah toa7 e5, chiu7-si7 chin Sin5 Siong7-te3. I e5 thiaN3 iaN5-ke3 pe7-bu2 e5 thiaN3 chin-choe7. Pe7-bu2 sui-jian5 si7 thiaN3 lan2, tan7-si7 in e5 thiaN3 u7 si5 iau2 si7 bo5 kong-piN5 e5; u7 e5 pe7-bu2 thiaN3 toa7-kiaN2, u7 e5 khah thiaN3 soe3-kiaN2; chan5-hoe3 e5, u7 e5 pe7-bu2 chiu7 khah khoaN3-khin i. 
  Na7-si7 Siong7-te3 e5 thiaN3 m7-si7 chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni. Siong7-te3 e5 thiaN3 si7 oan5-choan5 kong-gi7 e5 thiaN3; bo5-lun7 si7 ho2-giah8 a2-si7 song3-hiong, u7 te7-ui7 a2-si7 bo5 te7-ui7, bak8-chiu bo5 khoaN3-kiN3 e5 lang5, phoa3-piN7 e5, chan5-hoe3 e5, toa7-lang5, gin2-na2, lam5-hu7 lo2-iu3, Siong7-te3 ia7 piN5-piN5 long2 si7 thiaN3 in. Hiah e5 u7 sin3 Chu2, bo5 sin3 Chu2 e5 lang5, kiaN5-ho2, kiaN5 phaiN2 e5, Siong7-te3 iu5-goan5 thiaN3 in; mui2-jit8 ia7 si7 hou7 in bi2-niu5, chhai3-se, kap jit8-kng, khong-khi3, oah8-mia7. Siong7-te3 e5 thiaN3 u7 sim2-mih8 piau2-hian7 kap hian2-beng5? Ng3-bang7 bo5 khoaN3 lan2 e5 choe7. Tng lan2 e5 choe7 chin tang7 eng-kai tioh8 si2 e5 si5, Siong7-te3 bo5 chhin-chhiuN7 koaN-hu2, chai-iaN2 lan2 u7 sim2-mih8 chho3-gou7 chiu7 lip8-khek ka7 lan2 pan7-choe7. Lan2 sui-jian5 hoan7-choe7, Siong7-te3 iau2 lau5 hoe2-kai2 e5 ki-hoe7 hou7 lan2; I ng3-bang7 lan2 u7 hoe2-kai2 e5 ki-hoe7; na7 bo5 hoe2-kai2, lan2 si2-au7 I chiah sim2-phoaN3 lan2. Che chiu7-si7 thau5 chit8 hang7 Siong7-te3 thiaN3 e5 piau2-hian7. Te7 2 hang7 thiaN3 e5 piau2-hian7, chiu7-si7 lan2 e5 choe7 chin tang7 eng-kai tioh8 si2 e5 si5, Siong7-te3 iu5-goan5 bo5 pang3-sak lan2, kam-goan7 chiong I e5 tok8-siN KiaN2 siuN2-su3 lan2, ui7-tioh8 lan2 tam-tng choe7, siu7 teng3 si2 ti7 sip8-ji7-ke3 teng2, siu7 it-chhe3 e5 kan-khou2. Seng3-keng kong2, 
  In-ui7 Siong7-te3 chiong tok8-siN e5 KiaN2 siuN2-su3 se3-kan, hou7 kiN3-na7 sin3 I e5 lang5 boe7 tim5-lun5, oe7 tit-tioh8 eng2-oah8. I thiaN3 se3-kan kau3 an2-ni ( Iok-han7 3 : 16 ). 
  Ia5-sou e5 thiaN3: 
  Siong7-te3 chhe Ia5-sou lai5 se3-kan si7 m7-si7 beh kap lan2 keng3-cheng I e5 te7-ui7, a2-si7 keng3-cheng ti7 su7-giap8 nih? A2-si7 beh hiong2-siu7 se3-kan e5 khoai3-lok8 nih? Tng Ia5-sou kang3-seng e5 si5 Hi-lut8 ong5 kong2, I si7 beh kap i cheng-chhu2 ong5-ui7 beh choe3 ong5, sou2-i2 Hi-lut8 ong5 eng7 chin-choe7 e5 ke3-bou5 beh hai7 Ia5-sou. Ia5-sou m7-si7 beh kap lan2 cheng-chhu2 te7-ui7, iah8 m7-si7 beh hiong2-siu7 se3-kan e5 khoai3-lok8. I iah8 m7-si7 beh choe3 se3-kan e5 ong5; I e5 kang3-seng te7 it si7 sun7-than3 Siong7-te3 e5 beng7-leng7; te7 ji7 si7 ui7-tioh8 jin5-lui7 e5 choe7, I ui7-tioh8 choe7-jin5 e5 choe7 siu7 khou2 chin-choe7, chin-choe7 lang5 boe7-oe7 kam2-sia7, ia7 m7-sin3 I si7 Siong7-te3 e5 tok8-siN KiaN2, sim7-chi3 iau2 u7 chin-choe7 lang5 kong-kek Ia5-sou, ham7-hai7 I, le2-me7 I, siong5-siong5 beh eng7 chioh8-thau5 tim3 I. 
  I kang3-seng lai5 kau3 se3-kan m7-na7 bo5 tit-tioh8 khoai3-lok8, ji5-chhiaN2 ia7 bo5 tit-tioh8 sim2-mih8 hiong2-siu7, lian5 khoa3 thau5-khak e5 sou2-chai7 ia7 bo5; hoan2-tng2 siu7 pek-hai7 choe7-choe7. Sui-jian5 chio2-chio2 lang5 oe7 ui7-tioh8 in e5 peng5-iu2 hi-seng ka-ki7, chong2-si7 ui7-tioh8 gi7 lai5 song3-sit siN3-mia7 e5 chi2-u7 Ia5-sou chit8 e5. I kam-goan7 ui7-tioh8 se3-kan lang5 e5 choe7 hi-seng siN3-mia7 ia7 bo5 oan3-than3, che chiu7-si7 i thiaN3-lang5 e5 piau2-hian7. Ia5-sou si7 Siong7-te3 e5 KiaN2; I siu7 teng3 si2 ti7 sip8-ji7-ke3 teng2, na7 m7-si7 kam-sim kheng2 ui7 lang5 hi-seng, I goan5-pun2 chiu7 u7 leng5-lek8 thoat-li7. Tan7-si7 I bo5 an2-ni choe3, I kam-goan7 ui7-tioh8 choe7-jin5 e5 choe7, m7-kiaN si2; choe3-au7 ti7 sip8-ji7-ke3 teng2 siu7 kau3 choe7-choe7 tiam2-cheng e5 thong3-khou2, jian5-au7 tng7-khui3 si2. I lau5-chhut po2-huih, soe2-chheng choe7-jin5 e5 choe7, kiN3-na7 sin3 I e5 lang5 long2 u7 hun7 I e5 kiu3-siok8. 
  U7 chit8 e5 kou3-su7: 
  U7 chit8 e5 gin2-na2 kap he2-chhia e5 su-ki chin siong-sek8. I mui2-jit8 beh khi3 hak8-hau7 thak8-chheh e5 si5 long2 tioh8 keng-ke3 he2-chhia-lou7. Tng i na7 beh keng-ke3 he2-chhia-lou7 e5 si5, na7 u7 khoaN3-kiN3 he2-chhia ti7 hng7-hng7 teh lai5, i chiu7 kap he2-chhia e5 su-ki phah chio-hou. 
  U7 chit8 jit8, chit e5 gin2-na2 kiaN5 kau3 he2-chhia-lou7 e5 si5, hut-jian5 khoaN3-kiN3 he2-chhia lou7 e5 kio5, keng-ke3 hong chhe, hou7 ak, ni5 ku2 geh8 chhim, i2-keng beh tng7-khi3 lah. I ia7 khoaN3-kiN3 hng7-hng7 u7 chit8 tai5 he2-chhia teh lai5 lah. Sou2-i2 i e5 sim chin tioh8-kip, kiaN-liau2 he2-chhia lai5 chiu7 poah8-loh8 kio5-e7. I chiu7 koaN2-kin2 chiong ka-ki7 e5 saN thiah chit8 te3 pou3 pak8 ti7 tek-a2 kiah8 koan5. Su-put-ti7 su-ki bo5 khoaN3-kiN3 e5 khoan2-sit, he2-chhia i2-keng khui kau3 gui5-hiam2 e5 sou2-chai7 lah. Chit8 e5 gin2-na2 khoaN3-kiN3 chit khoan2 e5 cheng5-heng5 chin gong5-ngiah8, m7-chai beh chaiN2-iuN7 kai2-koat. Hit e5 gin2-na2 chi2-u7 sim chin chhiat, ai3 kiu3 i sou2 thiaN3 e5 su-ki, kap he2-chhia lai7 e5 lang5-kheh; i chiu7 ke3-siok8 koh kiaN5 khah kun7 lai5 iat8 i e5 pou3. Kho2-lin5, hit e5 gin2-na2 chiu7 ui7 liau2 an2-ni hou7 he2-chhia kheh-si2 lah. 
  He2-chhia lai7 u7 lang5 u7 khoaN3-kiN3 an2-ni, chiu7 thong-ti su-ki theng5 he2-chhia. Tng he2-chhia theng5 khi2-lai5 e5 si5, he2-chhia i2-keng kun7-oa2 ti7 choe3-au7 e5 chit8 pou7 e5 sou2-chai7 lah. Choe7-choe7 lang5-kheh loh8-chhia chai gin2-na2 si2-khi3 e5 goan5-in, si7 beh kiu3 in long2-chong2 e5 lang5, chiu7 choe7-choe7 lang5 siu7 kam2-tong7 lah. 
  Chhia-lai7 na7 u7 900 lang5, an2-ni chiu7-si7 kong2 hit e5 gin2-na2 kiu3 900 lang5 lah. I e5 hi-seng hou7 900 lang5 chiam7-si5 koh oah8 kui2-na7 ni5 ti7 chit se3-kan, chong2-si7 chit e5 gin2-na2 ia7 boe7 oe7 kiu3 hiah e5 900 lang5 e5 leng5-hun5 bian2 loh8 te7-gek8. 
  Ia5-sou e5 hi-seng: 
  Chu2 Ia5-sou e5 kiu3-siok8 m7-si7 chhin-chhiuN7 hit e5 gin2-na2 na7-tiaN7, I e5 hi-seng ia7 m7-si7 chi2-u7 beh kiu3 PhiN5-ou5 e5 lang5 na7-tiaN7, ia7 m7-si7 beh kiu3 Han3-bin5-chok8 na7-tiaN7. I e5 hi-seng si7 ui7-tioh8 choan5 se3-kai3 e5 lang5, mui2 si5-tai7 e5 lang5. I e5 kiu3-siok8 m7-si7 beh hou7 lang5 iong2-kiaN7, toa7 than3-chiN5, a2-si7 beh hou7 lang5 ho2 sin-mia7 na7-tiaN7; I e5 hi-seng si7 beh hou7 kiN3-na7 sin3 I e5 lang5 e5 leng5-hun5 boe7 tim5-lun5, oe7 tit-tioh8 eng2-oah8. 
  Sou2-i2 lan2 sin3 Chu2 e5 lang5, choe3-toa7 choe3-au7 e5 ng3-bang7 m7-si7 ti7 chit se3-kan; in-ui7 chit se3-kan e5 ng3-bang7 long2 si7 chiam7-si5 e5, chiong-lai5 ia7 si7 kui ti7 khang-khang. Choe3-toa7 e5 ng3-bang7 eng-kai khng3 ti7 chiong-lai5 Thian-kok e5 hok-khi3; ti7 hia bo5 iu-bun7, bo5 hoan5-lo2, bo5 lau5 bak8-sai2, bo5 piN7-thiaN3; ti7 hia chiah u7 eng2-oan2 e5 peng5-an kap khoai3-lok8. 
  Chin kho2-sioh, hian7-chai7 u7 chin choe7 lang5 in goan5-pun2 chiu7 chai-iaN2 u7 chin Sin5 Siong7-te3, tan7-si7 in-ui7 in m7-sin3 Siong7-te3. Chai koh m7-sin3, chit e5 choe7 chin-chiaN3 si7 tang7 ah! Tong-jian5 ia7 u7 choe7-choe7 bo5 beh sin3 si2-au7 leng5-hun5 e5 sim2-phoaN3. 
  In chai u7 chit8 tiau5 leng5-hun5, chong2-si7 m7-chai beh chaiN2-iuN7 choe3; chaiN2-iuN7 siat-hoat in e5 leng5-hun5 e5 kui-siok. Koh m7 chiap-siu7 sin3 e5 lang5 e5 oe7-gu2. Kho2-lin5 bo5 kho2-lin5! 
  Seng3-keng u7 ki3-chai3, Ia5-sou koh-oah8 hou7 To-ma2 khoaN3-kiN3 e5 si5 ka7 To-ma2 kong2: 
  Li2 in-ui7 khoaN3-kiN3 goa2 chiah sin3, hiah e5 bo5 khoaN3-kiN3 lai5 sin3 e5 lang5 u7 hok-khi3 ( Iok-han7 20 : 26 ). 
  ChhiaN2 lan2 lai5 gim5-si 490 siu2: 
  1 .Te3 Chu2 e5 lang5 u7 heng7-hok, <BR>Na2 chun2 iu5-siuN2 chin khoai3-lok8; <BR>Tak8 si5-khek o-lo2 gim5-si, <BR>Moa2 sim peng5-an chin tek-i3.
   ( Ho5 ) <BR>Oe7 tit khoai3-lok8, <BR>te3 Chu2 e5 lang5 khoai3-lok8, <BR>Chu2 e5 khoai3-lok8 bo5 thang pi2, <BR>Sim-toe2 tio5-thiau3 toa7 hoaN-hi2, <BR>KhiN5-tiau5 Chu2 m7-thang pang3-li7, chiu7 tit khoai3-lok8, <BR>Eng2-oan2 thang tit Chu2 khoai3-lok8. 
  2 .Te3 Chu2 e5 lang5 u7 heng7-hok, <BR>Khah-iaN5 khou2-thang3 tit khoai3-lok8; <BR>Tit Chu2 hok-im jip8 goa2 sim, <BR>Chhui3 boe7 kim3-tit khui siaN gim5. 
  3. Te3 Chu2 e5 lang5 u7 heng7-hok, <BR>Sui-jian5 kiaN5 ou-am3 soaN-kok; <BR>Na7 te3 Ia5-sou e5 kha-pou7, <BR>Oe7 tit Chu2 ka7 lan2 chhoa7 lou7. <BR>A-men. 
